  "keyFeatures": [
    "EcoBot AI chat assistant powered by Google Gemini / OpenRouter with image analysis for recycling identification",
    "Interactive map of recycling points (puntos de reciclaje) using Leaflet and Google Maps API",
    "Eco-game (WebGL Unity build) with leaderboard, achievements, and gamification points",
    "JWT + Google OAuth 2.0 authentication with email verification flow",
    "Real-time admin notifications and online user tracking via Socket.io",
    "Role-based access control (user / admin / superadmin)",
    "Automatic content moderation in AI chat with inappropriate-content detection and auto-ban",
    "Audit log system for admin actions",
    "Cloudinary-powered image uploads for carousel slides and recycling points",
    "Monorepo with pnpm workspaces (Express 5 backend + Vite/React 19 frontend)"
  ],
